EmailTemplate.description: Emails a MP info request after a survey is filled out requesting opportunity to donate to future projects
EmailTemplate.name: HH WF Students Donor trip follow up request
EmailTemplate.subject: You can help make future projects possible
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hi {!QPRO_Survey__c.contact_name__c},
Thanks so much for being willing to support our programs!
We're so excited that you're interested in donating, but we want to make sure that your parents or guardians are aware of your decision, so please share this information with them. You might need them to fill out some of the necessary financial information on your behalf, or they may be interested in helping you support us themselves!
The best way to help is by becoming a monthly partner, where you commit to donating an amount that is manageable for you each month, say $10, $20 or $50, which still adds up to a lot in the end, and helps us by having a consistent base of support for our projects throughout the year.
For example, donating $10 a month adds up to $120 after 12 months, which is enough to build a safe and clean bathroom for a family in Mexico, ensuring sanitation for an entire household! Or, donating $50 a month adds up to $600 over the year, which is enough to purchase medical supplies for a Live Different Build trip, helping to bring medical and dental services to communities that are without life-saving care!
To become a monthly partner, please contact our office at (866) 432 4464.
If you are unable to commit to being a monthly partner, we still welcome your one-time donation! Please note that we are in the process of setting up our online giving process, so for now you will need to call our office to donate. (866) 432 4464
If you or your parents have any questions at all, please do not hesitate to contact me.
Thanks again! Your support truly is life-changing!
Sincerely,
Cindy Stover Community Engagement Coordinator Live Different cindy@livedifferent.com 1-866-432-4464
